                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-144-18521213 t18521213-144-punishment-53"></join>Confined Four Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The sergeant stated that the prisoner did not bear a good character in the regiment, although no charge of dishonesty had been made against him before.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
